reviewText: Amazon sells basically the exact same video under different product names with vastly different prices. This is very deceptive and it is too bad Amazon has no quality control over such practices. This product is the same as...Stock Market Options Trading Education - Professional High Probability...as well as another video.  I have no problem with the videos, they are good,

wow,
